          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Benefits you deserve\nOpen a Bridgewater Bank Smart eSavings Account and benefit from features including:\nInitial deposit requirement only $25\nHigh interest savings account with a highly competitive rate\nInterest is calculated daily on the closing balance and compounded monthly directly into your Smart eSavings Account.\nWith pre-authorized contributions, you can \u2018set it and forget it\u2019.\nNo minimum ongoing balance required\nEasy transfer of funds from other financial institutions\nEligible for CDIC deposit insurance\nOne free withdrawal per month 2",
