        {
          "field_name": "deposit_insurance",
          "candidate_value": "CDIC Deposit Insurance Bridgewater Bank is a member of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation (CDIC).",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-ad0c420e2c7048b5",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "CDIC Deposit Insurance\nBridgewater Bank is a member of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation (CDIC). Eligible deposits, including the Smart eSavings\u2122 Account, are insured by CDIC up to $100,000 per depositor, per insured category, subject to CDIC rules and eligibility criteria. For more information about CDIC coverage, visit www.cdic.ca .\nNeed more information? Please see your Smart eSavings Account Agreement for your Smart eSavings account.\nQuestions? Please contact us .\n2 With the Smart eSavings account you are entitled to one free withdrawal per calendar month. There is a $5 service fee per transaction for additional withdrawals per calendar month.",
