        {
          "field_name": "eligibility_text",
          "candidate_value": "How to apply for a high-interest savings account To start the exciting journey towards watching your money grow with the Bridgewater Bank Smart eSavings\u2122 Account you must confirm the following information: Be a Canadian resident over the age of majority in your province",
