          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-0bf1494773c9b87b",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "How to apply for a high-interest savings account\nTo start the exciting journey towards watching your money grow with the Bridgewater Bank Smart eSavings\u2122 Account you must confirm the following information:\nBe a Canadian resident over the age of majority in your province.\nHave an existing chequing or savings account with a Canadian financial institution.\nThen please have the following information available prior to applying:\nEmployment information.\nSocial Insurance Number (SIN).\nA personal cheque from a bank account in your name (to deposit funds into your new Smart eSavings account). The cheque must be made payable to Bridgewater Bank in Canadian funds. Your name must be preprinted on the top left corner and cheques from a business account cannot be accepted.\nPlease contact us at the customer experience centre to apply, we\u2019ll help you through the application process and answer any",
