          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-672c393320bf6e17",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "Set up your pre-authorized contribution\nIt\u2019s easy to set up pre-authorized contributions. Simply choose the amount you\u2019d like to save and how often. That\u2019s it. The only thing easier is sitting back and watching your savings grow!\nAutomatic withdrawals can be set up when you open your account or created later by completing a Pre Authorized Debit (PAD) Agreement . You can change the frequency or amount of your contributions at any time simply by submitting a new PAD agreement 1 .\nFunds can be transferred from your external bank account to your Bridgewater Bank Smart eSavings Account on a monthly, semi-monthly, weekly, bi-weekly, quarterly or annual basis. And you can start with as little as $25.\nSet up a pre-authorized contribution today! Contact us for more information.\n1 The changes to your new PAD/PAC agreement will take about 15 business days.",
